What you need to know:

With both James (ankle) and Davis nursing nagging injuries, getting 54 points from their bench and holding the Rockets to just 46 points in the first half is good sign for the future. Davis also had three blocks."Our goal is to be the No. 1 defensive team in the league," said James. "We came in with the mindset to get stops and get out and do what we do on offense. We able to those things on both sides.